(8,'index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=8','index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=8:4-clear-signs-your-business-is-ready-to-grow&catid=2','4 Clear Signs Your Business Is Ready To Grow',' No matter the size of your company, good communication is essential. Maintaining high levels of productivity requires open lines of communication between you and your employees. ','2023-11-24 08:45:12','c4cefa458c7efa54942b4e344a0a6db8',1,1,1,'*','2023-11-09 02:44:24',NULL,'2023-11-09 02:44:24',NULL,0,0,3,'O:52:\"Joomla\\Component\\Finder\\Administrator\\Indexer\\Result\":19:{i:0;i:1;i:1;s:5:\"en-GB\";i:2;s:179:\" No matter the size of your company, good communication is essential. Maintaining high levels of productivity requires open lines of communication between you and your employees. \";i:3;a:27:{s:2:\"id\";i:8;s:5:\"alias\";s:44:\"4 clear signs your business is ready to grow\";s:7:\"summary\";s:188:\"<p>No matter the size of your company, good communication is essential. Maintaining high levels of productivity requires open lines of communication between you and your employees. </p>\r\n\";s:4:\"body\";s:1617:\"\r\n<p>The art of makeup has been an integral part of human civilisation for millennia. Ancient civilisations, from the Mesopotamians to the Romans, utilised cosmetics not just for beautification, but also as a reflection of status, health, and societal roles.</p>\r\n<h3>Increased Job Opportunities</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Access to an extra bedroom</li>\r\n<li>Increase your property value </li>\r\n<li>Extra space for storage</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Working remotely can also help you achieve a better work-life balance. When you have the flexibility to work from anywhere, you can more easily integrate work into your life. This can allow you to pursue personal interests and hobbies, while still being able to work and earn a living.</p>\r\n<p>Additionally, working remotely can reduce stress and improve mental health, since you have more control over your environment 